        "urls" : [ ],
        "text" : "I think this is an interesting assumption, but I'd like to see some evidence that this is true.  Generally, there seems to be an inverse correlation between wealth and fertility, just like between wealth and optimism.  I'd like to see some data supporting increase in manufacturing base can improve fertility.",
        "mentions" : [ ],
